snippet.title: Duck Souls - iOS and Android Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-Order link on iOS 50% off:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/duck-souls/id1567392764

Duck Souls is a fast-paced, action platformer about a little duck with an incredible skill to dash and a mission: find all the lost eggs in order to save his species.

Duck Souls is set in cute and deadly fantasy world, where many hazards will try to cut your wings off your body while you struggle to find all lost eggs, and keep your species alive. Run, jump and dash through a colorful and treacherous environment to save everyone and become a hero.
